== Multiple layouts ==

The feature introduced in XFree86 4.3.0. It allows to concatenate one-group symbol descriptions into the complex, up to 4 groups (hard limit by XKB) layouts.

Currently this feature is supported by
	* <a href="http://www.xfree.org/rel430.html">XFree86 Release 4.3.0</a>
	* <a href="http://freedesktop.org/~xorg/X11R6.7.0/doc/RELNOTES.html">X.Org Release 6.7.0</a>
	* <a href="http://www.xfree.org/rel440.html">XFree86 Release 4.4.0</a>

More about this feature read <a href`"http://pdx.freedesktop.org/~xklavier/xkbconfig.pdf">here in PDF</a> or <a href`"http://pdx.freedesktop.org/~xklavier/xkbconfig.sxw">here in OOo format</a>. 

